  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
  https://github.com/vercel/streamdown

Modifications by conciv:
  - Ported from React to SolidJS (render layer rebuilt on solid-markdown).
  - src/parse-blocks.ts is derived from streamdown's lib/parse-blocks.tsx
    (block-splitting algorithm unchanged; TS lint pragmas removed,
    index-access guards added for our stricter tsconfig).
  - src/animate.ts is derived from streamdown's lib/animate.ts
    (rehype fade-in plugin unchanged; the per-instance function-name dance
    was removed since we run one plugin instance per block).

